.com/manage/webhooks)\n5. Profit \ud83c\udf89\n\n**\ud83d\udc4b Hello! I'm Audun / xqus** \n\ud83d\udd17 My work: [xqus.com](https://xqus.com)\n\ud83d\udcb8 n8n shop: [xqus.gumroad.com](https://xqus.gumroad.com)\n\n### Want to trigger my workflow?\nSupport my work on [Ko-fi](https://ko-fi.com/xquscom) \ud83d\udcb8", "height": 400, "width": 860, "color": 1}, "typeVersion": 1}], "connections": {"Prepare": {"main": [[{"node": "Check token", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}, "Webhook": {"main": [[{"node": "Prepare", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}, "Check type": {"main": [[{"node": "Donation", "type": "main", "index": 0}], [{"node": "Subscription", "type": "main", "index": 0}], [{"node": "Shop Order", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}, "Check token": {"main": [[{"node": "Check type", "type": "main", "index": 0}], [{"node": "Stop and Error", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}, "Subscription": {"main": [[{"node": "Is new subscriber?", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}}, "settings": {}, "nodeGroups": []}, "customData": {}, "_source": "/tmp/n8n_corpus/DragonJAR_n8n-workflows-esp/workflows/03239-Process-Ko-fi-donations-subscriptions-shop-orders-with-webhook-verification.json"}